		<div>Scout mobs can see through sneak most frequently, level is a factor as mentioned and level of your sneak ability is a factor as well.<br />
<br />
There has been enough inconsistencies noted that there are other unknown and potentially unknowable factors to prevent sneak from becoming too reliable as SoS was when first implemented.<br />
<br />
Since you've deleted the Scout it doesn't really matter now, but all 6 quests that you could have been attempting in order to be able to advance to Level 10 and beyond have all been completed many times and are indeed possible.</div>
	</td>
