		<div>It's also completely unecessary to sneak to that area, you just have to get in proximity of the camp, and it's not difficult to avoid what few aggro goblinsa re along the way. I believe that NPC was using the word in it's general sense, not refering to the specific ability.<br />
<br />
I found sneak of very limited use on hte Isle because the mobs that are aggro can see through it until you are level 5 or six, by which point you are nearly ready, if not more so, to leave. Upgrade it to App3 as soon as you can, it makes a big difference (assuming you re-roll and try again).</div>
